content: Do you know any jokes about weddings?

I've got one for you! Why did the wedding planner quit her job? Because she found out it was just a sham! Okay, maybe that's a bit dark. How about this one: Why don't scientists trust atoms at weddings? Because they make up everything! Hey, I tried my best with wedding jokes. They're not my forte, but I hope you got a chuckle out of those.
